item.description:
## Case Status

A case can have one of the following status:

- **accepted**: the case was accepted by a MD clinician. When a case is accepted all the case prescriptions are created on DoseSpot side and are automatically sent to the pharmacies;
- **support**: the MD clinician transferred the case to support;
- **pending**: the case is waiting for a MD clinician to review it.

